## Healthcare Data Disclaimer

This software is designed to handle healthcare-related data and mortality information. 
Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with applicable healthcare regulations 
including but not limited to HIPAA, GDPR, and local privacy laws when using this 
software with real patient or mortality data.

The CTBAL platform processes mortality data from public sources (Find-a-Grave) and 
converts it into anonymized clinical research opportunities. All personal identifying 
information should be properly hashed or encrypted before blockchain storage.

## Academic and Research Use

This project is intended for academic research, clinical study advancement, and 
healthcare blockchain innovation. Commercial use for patient care should involve 
appropriate medical oversight and regulatory approval.